# Implementation Plan - Habit Tracker Polish & Completion

The Daily Habit Tracker is functional but lacks key features (Edit/Delete) and needs a UI polish to meet "premium" standards. This plan outlines the steps to complete the application.

## User Review Required
> [!IMPORTANT]
> I will be adding "Delete" and "Edit" buttons. Please confirm if you want these directly on the Dashboard or only in the Detail view to keep the main interface clean. **Current assumption: Delete/Edit in Detail view, simple Toggle in Dashboard.**

