- [ ] Add `deleteHabit(id)` function.
- [ ] Add `editHabit(id, newText)` function.
- [ ] Pass these functions to [HabitDetail](file:///c:/Users/admin/.gemini/%EC%8A%A4%EC%9C%84%EC%B9%98%EC%9B%B9%EC%84%9C%EB%B9%84%EC%8A%A4/daily-habit-tracker/src/HabitDetail.jsx#3-98) via routes.

